const objectCreate = (Ctor, ...rest) => {
  const obj = Object.create(Ctor.prototype);
  const res = Ctor.apply(obj, rest);
  return typeof res === 'object' ? res : obj;
}
const obj = objectCreate(Object, { a: 1 }); // Ê®°Êãü new
